>до</span><span> </span><span>використання</span><span> </span><span>даних</span><span> </span><span>про</span><span> </span><span>минулу</span><span> </span><span>поведінку</span><span> </span><span>та</span><span> </span><span>обміну</span><span> </span><span>результатами</span><span> </span><span>між</span><span> </span><span>пристроями</span><span> </span><span>—</span><span> </span><span>це</span><span> </span><span>відбувається</span><span> </span><span>миттєво</span><span>, </span><span>і</span><span> </span><span>більшість</span><span> </span><span>із</span><span> </span><span>нас</span><span> </span><span>навіть</span><span> </span><span>не</span><span> </span><span>замислюються</span><span> </span><span>про&nbsp;<em>роль</em></span><span> </span><span>штучного</span><span> </span><span>інтелекту</span><span> </span><span>в</span><span> </span><span>цьому</span><span>. </span><span>Тіз</span><span> </span><span>передбачає</span><span> </span><span>застосування</span><span> </span><span>подібних</span><span> </span><span>технологій</span><span> </span><span>у</span><span> </span><span>діагностиці</span><span>.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>\"</span><span>Уявіть</span><span>, </span><span>що</span><span> </span><span>ви</span><span> </span><span>йдете</span><span> </span><span>в</span><span> </span><span>лікарню</span><span> </span><span>на</span><span> </span><span>томографію</span><span> </span><span>або</span><span> </span><span>МРТ</span><span>, </span><span>—</span><span> </span><span>розповідає</span><span> </span><span>Скотт</span><span> </span><span>Тіз</span><span> (Scott Tease), </span><span>виконавчий</span><span> </span><span>директор</span><span> </span><span>відділу</span><span> </span><span>високопродуктивних</span><span> </span><span>обчислень</span><span> </span><span>і</span><span> </span><span>штучного</span><span> </span><span>інтелекту</span><span> Lenovo. </span><span>—</span><span> </span><span>Перш</span><span> </span><span>ніж</span><span> </span><span>зображення</span><span> </span><span>потрапить</span><span> </span><span>до</span><span> </span><span>лікаря</span><span> </span><span>або</span><span> </span><span>лаборанта</span><span>, </span><span>алгоритм</span><span> </span><span>обробить</span><span> </span><span>дані</span><span> </span><span>та</span><span> </span><span>позначить</span><span> </span><span>усі</span><span> </span><span>відхилення</span><span>. </span><span>Це</span><span> </span><span>прискорить</span><span> </span><span>роботу</span><span> </span><span>медиків</span><span>, </span><span>допоможе</span><span> </span><span>їм</span><span> </span><span>швидше</span><span> </span><span>виявити</span><span> </span><span>проблеми</span><span> </span><span>та</span><span> </span><span>нічого</span><span> </span><span>не</span><span> </span><span>пропустити</span><span>. </span><span>Зараз</span><span> </span><span>усі</span><span> </span><span>пов</span><span>'</span><span>язані</span><span> </span><span>з</span><span> </span><span>цим</span><span> </span><span>питання</span><span> </span><span>перебувають</span><span> </span><span>на</span><span> </span><span>розгляді</span><span> </span><span>регулюючих</span><span> </span><span>органів</span><span>\".</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in; text-align: center;\"><span><img alt=\"\" src=\"assets/build-in-contents/images/AI1.jpg\" style=\"height: 317px; width: 600px;\"></span></p> \n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span>Висока</span><span> </span><span>роздільна</span><span> </span><span>здатність</span><span> </span><span>і</span><span> </span><span>розширений</span><span> </span><span>аналіз</span><span> </span><span>дадуть</span><span> </span><span>змогу</span><span> </span><span>проводити</span><span> </span><span>віддалене</span><span> </span><span>сканування</span><span> </span><span>та</span><span> </span><span>діагностику</span><span> </span><span>й</span><span> </span><span>виявляти</span><span> </span><span>навіть</span><span> </span><span>найменші</span><span> </span><span>симптоми</span><span>.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Лікарі</span><span> </span><span>можуть</span><span> </span><span>сприйняти</span><span> </span><span>таке</span><span> </span><span>використання</span><span> </span><span>штучного</span><span> </span><span>інтелекту</span><span>, </span><span>але</span><span> </span><span>як</span><span> </span><span>щодо</span><span> </span><span>потоку</span><span> </span><span>даних</span><span> </span><span>відстеження</span><span>? </span><span>Пристрої</span><span> </span><span>для</span><span> </span><span>відстеження</span><span> </span><span>стану</span><span> </span><span>здоров</span><span>'</span><span>я</span><span>, </span><span>які</span><span> </span><span>автоматично</span><span> </span><span>повідомляють</span><span> </span><span>медичні</span><span> </span><span>заклади</span><span> </span><span>про</span><span> </span><span>можливі</span><span> </span><span>проблеми</span><span>, </span><span>викликали</span><span> </span><span>чимало</span><span> </span><span>подиву</span><span>.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>\"</span><span>Існує</span><span> </span><span>реальна</span><span> </span><span>стурбованість</span><span> </span><span>щодо</span><span> </span><span>можливої</span><span> </span><span>великої</span><span> </span><span>кількості</span><span> </span><span>помилкових</span><span> </span><span>попереджень</span><span>, </span><span>і</span><span> </span><span>в</span><span> </span><span>найближчому</span><span> </span><span>майбутньому</span><span>, </span><span>найімовірніше</span><span>, </span><span>нічого</span><span> </span><span>не</span><span> </span><span>зміниться</span><span>, </span><span>—</span><span> </span><span>розповідає</span><span> </span><span>доктор</span><span> </span><span>Ден</span><span> </span><span>Стівенс</span><span> (Dan Stevens), </span><span>колишній</span><span> </span><span>лікар</span><span> </span><span>і</span><span> </span><span>менеджер</span><span> </span><span>із</span><span> </span><span>медичної</span><span> </span><span>продукції</span><span> </span><span>в</span><span> Lenovo. </span><span>—</span><span> </span><span>Імовірно</span><span>, </span><span>діагности</span><span> </span><span>оцінять</span><span> </span><span>переваги</span><span> </span><span>оперативних</span><span> </span><span>даних</span><span> </span><span>із</span><span> </span><span>портативних</span><span> </span><span>пристроїв</span><span>, </span><span>які</span><span> </span><span>вони</span><span> </span><span>зможуть</span><span> </span><span>отримувати</span><span> </span><span>за</span><span> </span><span>запитом</span><span>\".</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>Крім</span><span> </span><span>того</span><span>, </span><span>зараз</span><span> </span><span>дедалі</span><span> </span><span>більше</span><span> </span><span>росте</span><span> </span><span>попит</span><span> </span><span>на</span><span> \"</span><span>зручні</span><span>\" </span><span>технології</span><span> </span><span>—</span><span> </span><span>усе</span><span>, </span><span>що</span><span> </span><span>дає</span><span> </span><span>змогу</span><span> </span><span>швидко</span><span> </span><span>отримати</span><span> </span><span>допомогу</span><span> </span><span>через</span><span> </span><span>програму</span><span> </span><span>або</span><span> </span><span>веб</span><span>-</span><span>сайт</span><span>. </span><span>Це</span><span> </span><span>допоможе</span><span> </span><span>змінити</span><span> </span><span>підхід</span><span> </span><span>до</span><span> </span><span>обслуговування</span><span> </span><span>без</span><span> </span><span>ризиків</span><span> </span><span>для</span><span> </span><span>пацієнтів</span><span>. </span><span>До</span><span> </span><span>таких</span><span> </span><span>технологій</span><span> </span